      ‚ćĚ socket communication: send 'Hello' from one socket to another socket
      ‚ćĚ and send 'World!' back.
      ‚ćĚ
      AF_INET     ‚Üź 2           ‚ćĚ see /usr/include/.../bits/socket.h
      SOCK_STREAM ‚Üź 1           ‚ćĚ see /usr/include/.../bits/socket_type.h
      IPPROTO_IP       ‚Üź 0      ‚ćĚ see /usr/include/netinet/in.h
      LOCALHOST‚Üź256‚ä•127 0 0 1   ‚ćĚ 127.0.0.1 in host byte order
      Port ‚Üź 22222
      Server‚ÜźAF_INET, LOCALHOST, Port

      ‚ćĚ socket(AF_INET, SOCK_STREAM, IPPROTO_IP)
      ‚ćĚ
      3 ‚Č§ Handle‚ÜźFIO‚ąÜsocket AF_INET, SOCK_STREAM, IPPROTO_IP
1

