      ‚ćĚ execve
      ‚ćĚ
      ‚ćĚFilename‚Üź'/usr/local/lib/apl/TLV_server'  ‚ćĚ whereever TLV_server lives
      Filename‚Üź'../tools/TLV_server'
      Handle ‚Üź FIO‚ąÜexecve Filename        ‚ćĚ start & connect TLV_server
      TLV ‚Üź 33 ‚éēCR 42,'Forty-Two'         ‚ćĚ encode a TLV buffer, Tag 42
      ‚ä£TLV ‚éēFIO[43] Handle                ‚ćĚ send TLV buffer to TLV_server
      TL ‚Üź 8 ‚éēFIO[6] Handle               ‚ćĚ read tag/lenght from TLV_server
      Value ‚Üź (256‚ä•4‚ÜďTL) ‚éēFIO[6] Handle   ‚ćĚ read value  from TLV_server
      34 ‚éēCR TL,Value                     ‚ćĚ display response tag and value
¬Į42 owT-ytroF
      TLV ‚Üź 33 ‚éēCR 99,'quit'              ‚ćĚ encode stop command, Tag 99
      ‚ä£TLV ‚éēFIO[43] Handle                ‚ćĚ send TLV buffer to TLV_server
      ‚ä£(‚éēFIO[4] Handle)                   ‚ćĚ close connection (stops TLV_server)

